com.github.seqware.queryengine.backInterfaces
Interface LowLevelBackEndInterface

All Known Subinterfaces:
BackEndInterface
All Known Implementing Classes:
HBasePersistentBackEnd, MRHBasePersistentBackEnd, SimplePersistentBackEnd
public interface LowLevelBackEndInterface

This interface specifies operations to persist, update, and add objects to the back-end without knowing about the specific database back-end. Should only be used by back-end developers

Version:
$Id: $Id
